When you're pulling a mob (or 2, or 3, or 20), don't bring it back to the group, but FD in range of the Main Assist's bow. <br>
He/She can then tag the current mob you have with you without much danger of getting adds.<br>
While this is going on, stay down, as many times I've gone to assist the party, and found I had some extra agro following me who decided to take the long way to us.<br>
<br>
Oh, and watch out for the ghoul's harm touch - 700hp gone in the blink of an eye.<br>
