<br>
Tag a roamer. any roamer, as long as he roams all over the place.<br>
<br>
FD a ways out from your group, within sight of your MT.<br>
<br>
Wait. After a min, stand up and the roamer will path to you, bringing lots of friends. just fd, and tell your mt when it's good to tag. when they're ready for more just stand up again.<br>
<br>
you can do a lot of fear this way if you find the right places it's actually pretty fun =p<br>
<br>
